headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Celebrate Independence Day
content:
Get in the swing of the flag-waving spirit with The Vapid Liberator, available to claim for free from Warstock Cache & Carry.

Show your patriotic flair with 50% off Independence Day-themed weapons, customizations, vehicles, and more.

Plus, get 2X GTA$ and RP on Smuggler Sell Missions.
